---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Servicios | Dakodev Software Solutions">
  <main class="pt-32 pb-20 relative z-10">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
        <div
          class="text-accent-cyan font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-4"
        >
          Especialización
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
          Nuestras <span class="text-gradient">Verticales</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <span
            class="text-gray-100 font-semibold border-b-2 border-accent-cyan/20"
            >Simplificamos lo complejo.</span
          > Desde la presencia digital hasta el núcleo operativo de tu empresa, nuestras
          soluciones están diseñadas para escalar.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- DAKO・WEB -->
        <div
          class="glass p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 hover:border-accent-cyan/50 transition-all duration-500 group relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col"
        >
          <div
            class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-3 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity"
          >
            <span
              class="text-9xl font-black text-accent-cyan leading-none -mr-4 -mt-4"
              >W</span
            >
          </div>

          <div
            class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent-cyan/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="w-7 h-7 text-accent-cyan"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mb-2">DAKO・WEB</h3>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <span
              class="px-3 py-1 bg-accent-cyan/10 text-accent-cyan rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide"
            >
              Para Profesionales
            </span>
          </div>

          <p
            class="text-gray-300 mb-8 pb-6 border-b border-white/10 text-lg leading-relaxed grow"
          >
            Tu web profesional lista para vender desde el primer día. <br />
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2 block"
              >Ideal para: Estudios, Agencias, Portfolios.</span
            >
          </p>

          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-accent-cyan mr-2 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Velocidad de carga inmediata.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-accent-cyan mr-2 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Diseño 100% optimizado para móviles.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-accent-cyan mr-2 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Sin mantenimiento técnico necesario.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- DAKO・CORE -->
        <div
          class="glass p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 hover:border-accent-blue/50 transition-all duration-500 group relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col"
        >
          <div
            class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-3 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity"
          >
            <span
              class="text-9xl font-black text-accent-blue leading-none -mr-4 -mt-4"
              >C</span
            >
          </div>

          <div
            class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent-blue/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="w-7 h-7 text-accent-blue"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mb-2">DAKO・CORE</h3>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <span
              class="px-3 py-1 bg-accent-blue/10 text-accent-blue rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide"
            >
              Para Negocios
            </span>
          </div>

          <p
            class="text-gray-300 mb-8 pb-6 border-b border-white/10 text-lg leading-relaxed grow"
          >
            Chau Excel. Control total de stock y ventas en un solo lugar.<br />
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2 block"
              >Ideal para: Comercios, Distribuidores.</span
            >
          </p>

          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-accent-blue mr-2 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Ventas, Compras y Stock integrados.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-accent-blue mr-2 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Facturación electrónica automática.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-accent-blue mr-2 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Acceso desde cualquier dispositivo.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- DAKO・HYBRID -->
        <div
          class="glass p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 hover:border-accent-teal/50 transition-all duration-500 group relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col"
        >
          <div
            class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-3 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity"
          >
            <span
              class="text-9xl font-black text-accent-teal leading-none -mr-4 -mt-4"
              >H</span
            >
          </div>

          <div
            class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent-teal/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="w-7 h-7 text-accent-teal"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M11 3.055A9.001 9.001 0 1020.945 13H11V3.055z"></path>
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M20.488 9H15V3.512A9.025 9.025 0 0120.488 9z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mb-2">DAKO・HYBRID</h3>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <span
              class="px-3 py-1 bg-accent-teal/10 text-accent-teal rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide"
            >
              Para Empresas
            </span>
          </div>

          <p
            class="text-gray-300 mb-8 pb-6 border-b border-white/10 text-lg leading-relaxed grow"
          >
            Sistemas a medida con lógica de negocio exclusiva y portales
            cliente.<br />
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2 block"
              >Ideal para: Empresas de Servicios, SaaS.</span
            >
          </p>

          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-accent-teal mr-2 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Portales de autogestión para clientes.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-accent-teal mr-2 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Integraciones complejas a medida.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-accent-teal mr-2 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Experiencia de usuario App-Like.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-20 text-center">
        <a
          href="/contacto/"
          class="px-8 py-4 bg-accent-cyan text-dark font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg shadow-accent-cyan/20 inline-flex items-center"
        >
          Solicitar Asesoría
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="h-5 w-5 ml-2"
            viewBox="0 0 20 20"
            fill="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
              clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
